{
  "stem": "268.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it wasn't a long ride.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was in one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came to this tech camp of Schoenbeck again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Same routine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Admission, you know-- given a-- a number, uniform, and a-- a job assignment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to myself, now the truth will come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They put me-- they put me on-- and it turn-- as it turn out to be, these were air crafts-- electric Henkels.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't find out until after liberation, they were making parts for-- you remember the Messerschmidt Junkers and then Henkels?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These were the air crafts that made Junkers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "J-U-- it's-- it's pronounced in German, 'Yun-kers.' And in English, it's 'Jun-kers,' J-U-N-K-E-R-S.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said-- and I said to myself, this time, I'm really-- this is going to be the end for me because they'll find out that I-- I was some kind of imposter.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the war for-- this is typical German-- German mentality.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "March of 1944, the-- the Russians are 200 kilometers from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Americans are nearing the Elbe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, and it's-- the-- the war can be counted in days now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had no idea, but they did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they still go through the motions of-- of qualifying you, of, you know, shipping you and of-- of making exams whether you're a real electrician.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and you know, and segregating and putting in separates-- and [? well, ?] they took us to these big hangers like.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one guy, he was telling us what we're going to do here, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we went back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Next day, we never showed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We never saw the hangars again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were bombed out, burned out.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
